Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.95,0:07:54.95,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}翻譯：spirit ZERO、NT000A；後期：zipwinmax。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那是」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.53,0:00:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「總數10名女主角贈送的」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.30,0:00:09.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「甜蜜難忘的戀愛故事」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.30,0:00:28.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「但是  不知為什麼  我現在感覺有點高興呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.48,0:00:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「涼宮春日」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.02,0:00:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「這個  借給你」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.48,0:00:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「長門有希」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.14,0:00:43.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「請稱呼我為實玖瑠吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.48,0:00:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「朝比奈實玖瑠」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:50.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你和我有同樣的氣息」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.48,0:00:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「鶴屋」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.48,0:00:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「朝倉涼子」「喜綠江美里」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.48,0:00:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「森園生」「妹妹」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:43.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.26,0:01:46.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒停呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.30,0:01:49.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨下個不停  都不能出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.82,0:01:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭呢  實玖瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.95,0:01:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.13,0:01:55.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對吧  就算沒下雨我們基本上也不出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.33,0:01:57.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:02:01.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很自信地記得活動時間大半都消磨在了遊戲上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.75,0:02:04.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…但是不對哦  阿虛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.18,0:02:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為晴天隨時可以出去  所以才故意待在活動室裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.01,0:02:11.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不成廢材了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.74,0:02:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:15.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上原因  今天就來換衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.16,0:02:19.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然說什麼呢  到底要我們穿什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.79,0:02:23.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我們  是要實玖瑠進行換裝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驚！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.81,0:02:25.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.86,0:02:29.69,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（第一回實玖瑠換裝大會）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.05,0:02:32.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那得考慮下服裝的款式了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.76,0:02:35.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那先畫作為基準的實玖瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:38.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是要在這上面畫衣服囉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.48,0:02:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.55,0:02:42.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.81,0:02:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是把腦中的映像原樣畫出來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:49.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模特就在那裡嘛  別依賴記憶了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.04,0:02:51.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊看邊畫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.48,0:02:59.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是處境變了而已！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:01.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.37,0:03:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀呵  實玖瑠在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.69,0:03:06.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  鶴屋同學  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.39,0:03:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀  看來很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:11.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我數學的筆記
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.60,0:03:12.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.99,0:03:16.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在動不了  你自己從書包裡拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:17.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是這樣子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.24,0:03:20.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢  笨蛋阿虛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.98,0:03:22.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子  一定是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.00,0:03:25.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？  好像有爭執呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.21,0:03:28.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  鶴屋學姐  來得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:30.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴屋學姐  幫幫忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:37.53,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「實玖瑠光線」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,途中開始都不知道在做什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.28,0:03:37.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來只靠我們是無法修正軌道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:39.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在拍特攝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  完全沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒什麼關係  不過特攝也不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電影第二彈就拍特攝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:48.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說明中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵  實玖瑠的換裝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:56.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是個不能錯過的活動啊  請務必讓我參加
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:03:59.13,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（鶴屋學姐追加）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.99,0:03:59.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴屋學姐參加的話就萬事大吉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:00.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.61,0:04:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴屋流肖像畫技巧可是被稱為如同照片般逼真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  馬上開始畫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:24.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個房間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.75,0:04:26.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才情況來看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:29.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經被涼宮春日的力量異空間化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:32.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法進行精確的作業
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.82,0:04:37.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來畫畫沒有狀態呢  要不停手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢  想其它方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:43.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它方法？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:45.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  鶴屋學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:48.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼  迅速開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:52.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人怎麼一臉邪惡的表情…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.65,0:04:56.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:04:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不錯不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.54,0:04:59.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特攝裝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:00.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼變成特攝了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.31,0:05:03.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的主題不是換裝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.46,0:05:04.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.66,0:05:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了  換裝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.47,0:05:09.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是換個說法而已吧  那是特攝裝！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:11.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼還需要怪獸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.82,0:05:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演員決定好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢…實玖瑠的對手果然應該是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:18.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣？  有希能行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:22.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…回答這麼直接行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.66,0:05:24.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.91,0:05:27.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經有過一次經驗了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.53,0:05:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.77,0:05:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.40,0:05:32.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…嗯  小心點…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.14,0:05:46.16,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（預定在文化祭上映（？））
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.77,0:05:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實玖瑠飛得再優雅點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:47.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼…涼宮同學！高！好高啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  古泉你這次沒來搗亂呢  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？ 啊  這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.32,0:05:59.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊  稍微在考慮些事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:03.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？  不  你沒有必要道歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.56,0:06:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道春日又發生什麼情況了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.29,0:06:10.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是關於涼宮同學的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.02,0:06:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  確實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.75,0:06:17.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事還是跟你說下比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.66,0:06:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總數10名的攻略對象女主角還剩兩個未定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道我也在其中？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:30.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想些什麼呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.69,0:06:32.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才就一直在糾結這個嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.90,0:06:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼還有一人就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.80,0:06:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新川先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.68,0:06:39.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣都行！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.36,0:06:41.89,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（打心底認為怎樣都行）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.61,0:06:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做出來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.79,0:06:46.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試玩就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:47.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:49.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【長門】「可以的話…」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.64,0:06:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是「消失」！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.31,0:06:53.07,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（因為是長門做的）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:55.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來到信上指定的地點  發現朝倉已經在那裡了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…朝倉路線嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.71,0:06:59.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要攻略她很難
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:02.72,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【朝倉】「我對你已經沒興趣了  所以…」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一個選擇錯誤…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.91,0:07:03.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會Bad End
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.72,0:07:05.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【朝倉】「死吧！！」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:05.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難度好高！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.49,0:07:09.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外這種類型的女主角叫養得累
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.58,0:07:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…我覺得大概不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.94,0:07:16.07,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不好  要遲到了」我咬著麵包跑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.11,0:07:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這展開模式還真是常見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.94,0:07:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【新川】「你！沒事吧？」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.10,0:07:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個邂逅方式太俗套了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:23.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是邂逅  這是事故啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.09,0:07:25.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這啥  新川先生路線！？
